TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.92</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg019.perseus-grc1:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.23</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; rarely in full, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κ. ἀπὸ τοῦ βήματος</foreign> ib.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">113</biblScope> </bibl>; so <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατάβα.--καταβήσομαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:979\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">979</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; later, also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κ. ἀπὸ τοῦ λόγου, ἀπὸ τῶν ἰαμβείων</foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to cease</tr_> from . . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg044:35\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tox.\">Tox.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">35</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg035:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nec.\">Nec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n53651.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> less freq. of things, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὶν . . καταβήμεναι ἐκ Διὸς οὖρον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</