.D.)</date>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:1:51\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.51</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n53651.11\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λέγεται μηδὲν αὐτοῖς τούτων καταβαίνειν</foreign>, of abusive language, does not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">affect</tr_> them or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">get home</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1264.tlg001:2:242\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Chrysipp.Stoic.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.242</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}